"  Crust:","1 cup all-purpose flour","1/8 teaspoon salt","2 tablespoons chilled butter or stick margarine, cut into small pieces","2 tablespoons vegetable shortening","3 tablespoons plus 1/2 teaspoon ice water","1 teaspoon cider vinegar","  Butter-flavored cooking spray","  Filling:","1 tablespoon butter or stick margarine","1/2 cup packed brown sugar","3/4 teaspoon ground cinnamon","9 cups sliced peeled Granny Smith apple (about 2 3/4 pounds)","3 tablespoons all-purpose flour","2 teaspoons lemon juice","  Topping:","1/4 cup all-purpose flour","1/4 cup packed brown sugar","2 tablespoons chilled butter or stick margarine, cut into small pieces","1/4 cup fat-free caramel sundae syrup"